description:
The first collection of Handsome Flappy

A big thank you to all early adopters!
All OG NFT owners will not be forgotten in the future, especially on the first sale. A big part of my concept is that owners of my NFT will get rewards of all kinds over time. We will see in which direction it develops. I dream of one Handsome Flappy real life doll. Would be incredibly awesome, wouldn't it?

Be a part of the community and support non-profit organizations at the same time.

Find out what is behind my project
https://HandsomeFlappy.com
